                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; position: relative;">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #2c5aa0; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 3px;"></i>
                                                    <strong style="color: #2c5aa0;">Tanggal:</strong> 4-5 Mei 2024
                                                </li>
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; position: relative;">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #2c5aa0; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 3px;"></i>
                                                    <strong style="color: #2c5aa0;">Waktu:</strong> 08.00 - 12.00 WIB
                                                </li>
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; position: relative;">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #2c5aa0; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 3px;"></i>
                                                    <strong style="color: #2c5aa0;">Tempat:</strong> Kampus Baitul Jannah Islamic School
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>Peserta diharapkan hadir 30 menit sebelum tes dimulai dan membawa perlengkapan sebagai berikut:</p>
